P(S_n < 1) = \int_0^1 f_n(s)\ ds =  \dfrac{1}{n!}
P(N=n) = P(S_{n-1} < 1 \le S_n) = P(S_{n-1} < 1) - P(S_n - 1) = \frac{1}{(n-1)!} - \frac{1}{n!} = \frac{n-1}{n!}
